## 🧱 PART 3 — MAKE PROXY PERSISTENT (SYSTEMD)

### STEP 1 — CREATE SERVICE

sudo nano /etc/systemd/system/ollama-proxy.service

---

### CONTENT

[Unit]
Description=Ollama Proxy Service
After=network.target

[Service]
ExecStart=/usr/bin/python3 /opt/ollama-proxy/ollama_proxy.py
WorkingDirectory=/opt/ollama-proxy
Restart=always
User=splunk
Environment=PYTHONUNBUFFERED=1

[Install]
WantedBy=multi-user.target

---

### STEP 2 — ENABLE + START

sudo systemctl daemon-reexec
sudo systemctl daemon-reload

sudo systemctl enable ollama-proxy
sudo systemctl start ollama-proxy

---

### STEP 3 — VERIFY

systemctl status ollama-proxy

Logs:
journalctl -u ollama-proxy -f

